##HTML Tables
A web table is an HTML structure which consists of multiple table rows with each row containing one or more table cells.
->Tables are block level elements.
->The size of the table is defined by the number of rows, cells and content.
<table> -> Defines table.
<tr>  -> Defines a row in a table.
<th>  -> Defines a header cell in a table.
<td>  -> Defines a cell in a table.


##What is an HTML Table?
HTML table is used to display data in rows and columns
Similar to an Excel spreadsheet
Tables are block-level elements

