ðŸ”¹ Table Structure
A table contains rows (<tr>)
Rows contain cells (<th> or <td>)
Table size depends on:
Number of rows
Number of columns
Content inside cells

ðŸ”¹ Table Attributes
border â†’ Adds border to table
